oteopening";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6035;}i:143;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:235:"Rahula, all the brahmans and contemplatives in the course of the past who purified their bodily acts, verbal acts, and mental acts, did it through repeated reflection on their bodily acts, verbal acts, and mental acts in just this way.";}i:2;i:6036;}i:144;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6271;}i:145;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"p_open";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6271;}i:146;a:3:{i:0;s:18:"doublequoteopening";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6273;}i:147;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:63:"All the brahmans and contemplatives in the course of the future";}i:2;i:6274;}i:148;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:6337;}i:149;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:210:" All the brahmans and contemplatives at present who purify their bodily acts, verbal acts, and mental acts, do it through repeated reflection on their bodily acts, verbal acts, and mental acts in just this way.";}i:2;i:6340;}i:150;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6550;}i:151;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"p_open";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6550;}i:152;a:3:{i:0;s:18:"doublequoteopening";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6552;}i:153;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:253:"Therefore, Rahula, you should train yourself: 'I will purify my bodily acts through repeated reflection. I will purify my verbal acts through repeated reflection. I will purify my mental acts through repeated reflection.' Thus you should train yourself.";}i:2;i:6553;}i:154;a:3:{i:0;s:18:"doublequoteclosing";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6806;}i:155;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6807;}i:156;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"p_open";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6807;}i:157;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:9:"— MN 61";}i:2;i:6809;}i:158;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6818;}i:159;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"p_open";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6818;}i:160;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:2:"¶";}i:2;i:6821;}i:161;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6823;}i:162;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"p_open";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6823;}i:163;a:3:{i:0;s:18:"doublequoteopening";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:6825;}i:164;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:106:"These five things are welcome, agreeable, pleasant, and hard to obtain in the world. Which five? Long life";}i:2;i:6826;}i:165;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:6932;}i:166;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:7:" beauty";}i:2;i:6935;}i:167;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:6942;}i:168;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:9:" pleasure";}i:2;i:6945;}i:169;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:6954;}i:170;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:7:" status";}i:2;i:6957;}i:171;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:6964;}i:172;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:18:" rebirth in heaven";}i:2;i:6967;}i:173;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:6985;}i:174;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:473:" Now, I tell you, these five things are not to be obtained by reason of prayers or wishes. If they were to be obtained by reason of prayers or wishes, who here would lack them? It's not fitting for the disciple of the noble ones who desires long life to pray for it or to delight in doing so. Instead, the disciple of the noble ones who desires long life should follow the path of practice leading to long life. In so doing, he will attain long life, either human or divine";}i:2;i:6988;}i:175;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:7461;}i:176;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:64:"(Similarly with beauty, pleasure, status, and rebirth in heaven)";}i:2;i:7464;}i:177;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:7528;}i:178;a:3:{i:0;s:18:"doublequoteclosing";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:7531;}i:179;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:7532;}i:180;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"p_open";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:7532;}i:181;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:11:"— AN 5.43";}i:2;i:7534;}i:182;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:7545;}i:183;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"p_open";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:7545;}i:184;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:2:"¶";}i:2;i:7548;}i:185;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:7550;}i:186;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"p_open";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:7550;}i:187;a:3:{i:0;s:18:"doublequoteopening";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:7552;}i:188;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:379:"Monks, these four types of kamma have been directly realized, verified, & made known by me. Which four? There is kamma that is dark with dark result. There is kamma that is bright with bright result. There is kamma that is dark & bright with dark & bright result. There is kamma that is neither dark nor bright with neither dark nor bright result, leading to the ending of kamma.";}i:2;i:7553;}i:189;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:7932;}i:190;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"p_open";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:7932;}i:191;a:3:{i:0;s:18:"doublequoteopening";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:7934;}i:192;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:659:"And what is kamma that is dark with dark result? There is the case where a certain person fabricates an injurious bodily fabrication, fabricates an injurious verbal fabrication, fabricates an injurious mental fabrication. Having fabricated an injurious bodily fabrication, having fabricated an injurious verbal fabrication, having fabricated an injurious mental fabrication, he rearises in an injurious world. On rearising in an injurious world, he is there touched by injurious contacts. Touched by injurious contacts, he experiences feelings that are exclusively painful, like those of the beings in hell. This is called kamma that is dark with dark result.";}i:2;i:7935;}i:193;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:8594;}i:194;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"p_open";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:8594;}i:195;a:3:{i:0;s:18:"doublequoteopening";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:8596;}i:196;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:139:"And what is kamma that is bright with bright result? There is the case where a certain person fabricates a non-injurious bodily fabrication";}i:2;i:8597;}i:197;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:8736;}i:198;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:35:" a non-injurious verbal fabrication";}i:2;i:8739;}i:199;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:8774;}i:200;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:35:" a non-injurious mental fabrication";}i:2;i:8777;}i:201;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:8812;}i:202;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:37:" He rearises in a non-injurious world";}i:2;i:8815;}i:203;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:8852;}i:204;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:46:" There he is touched by non-injurious contacts";}i:2;i:8855;}i:205;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:8901;}i:206;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:149:" He experiences feelings that are exclusively pleasant, like those of the Ever-radiant Devas. This is called kamma that is bright with bright result.";}i:2;i:8904;}i:207;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:9053;}i:208;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"p_open";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:9053;}i:209;a:3:{i:0;s:18:"doublequoteopening";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:9055;}i:210;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:173:"And what is kamma that is dark & bright with dark & bright result? There is the case where a certain person fabricates a bodily fabrication that is injurious & non-injurious";}i:2;i:9056;}i:211;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:9229;}i:212;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:55:" a verbal fabrication that is injurious & non-injurious";}i:2;i:9232;}i:213;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:9287;}i:214;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:55:" a mental fabrication that is injurious & non-injurious";}i:2;i:9290;}i:215;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:9345;}i:216;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:50:" He rearises in an injurious & non-injurious world";}i:2;i:9348;}i:217;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:9398;}i:218;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:58:" There he is touched by injurious & non-injurious contacts";}i:2;i:9401;}i:219;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"entity";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:3:"...";}i:2;i:9459;}i:220;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:226:" He experiences injurious & non-injurious feelings, pleasure mingled with pain, like those of human beings, some devas, and some beings in the lower realms. This is called kamma that is dark & bright with dark & bright result.";}i:2;i:9462;}i:221;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:9688;}i:222;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"p_open";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:9688;}i:223;a:3:{i:0;s:18:"doublequoteopening";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:9690;}i:224;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:367:"And what is kamma that is neither dark nor bright with neither dark nor bright result, leading to the ending of kamma? right view, right resolve, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, right concentration. This is called kamma that is neither dark nor bright with neither dark nor bright result, leading to the ending of kamma.";}i:2;i:9691;}i:225;a:3:{i:0;s:18:"doublequoteclosing";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:10058;}i:226;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:10059;}i:227;a:3:{i:0;s:6:"p_open";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:10059;}i:228;a:3:{i:0;s:5:"cdata";i:1;a:1:{i:0;s:12:"— AN 4.235";}i:2;i:10061;}i:229;a:3:{i:0;s:7:"p_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:10073;}i:230;a:3:{i:0;s:13:"section_close";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:10073;}i:231;a:3:{i:0;s:12:"document_end";i:1;a:0:{}i:2;i:10073;}}